reaction.comment: ! This section contains air-plasma chemistry, including
! VV and VT processes for N2
! This reaction is to work around a bug in ChemKin parsing
! which applies the wrong units to the reaction before a new REACTIONS block.
! Ar plasma: reactions of electronically excited species
! Piper 1973 gives total quenching by CH4 of 0.33e-9 cm^3/s
! Jauberteau 1997 gives ratio of about 1:2 for these two product branches
! Matches total rate coeff from Sekiya 1990, and reaction path is same as in Lombardi 2004
! Piper 1973 - split half and half with below
! vandDeSanden 1993 - estimated due to Te dependence
! Charge? Products from Lombardi 2004, rate from Chatham 1983
! This reaction is to work around a bug in ChemKin parsing
! which applies the wrong units to the reaction before a new REACTIONS block.
! C. WESTBROOK'S MECHANISM, UNITS: CM3/MOL/S, CAL, K
! MARINOV, N. M., PITZ, W. J., WESTBROOK, C. K., VINCITORE, A. M.,
! CASTALDI, M. J., SENKAN, S. M. "AROMATIC AND POLYCYCLIC AROMATIC
! HYDROCARBON FORMATION IN A LAMINAR PREMIXED N-BUTANE FLAME"
! C. WESTBROOK'S MECHANISM, UNITS: CM3/MOL/S, CAL, K
! MARINOV, N. M., PITZ, W.J., WESTBROOK, C.K., HORI, M., AND MATSUNAGA, N.
! "AN EXPERIMENTAL AND KINETIC CALCULATION OF THE PROMOTION EFFECT OF HYDROCARBONS
! ON THE NO-NO2 CONVERSION IN A FLOW REACTOR",
